# Bot Commands
__**Dinosaur**__
type </dino:930896048149381120> to get a random Dinosaur fact.

__**Ian Malcolm Quotes**__
type </ianquote:1362059542338474157> to get a random quote by Ian Malcolm from Jurassic Park

__**Tickets**__
type </ticket:967419478176583710>, which will invoke a Modal, where you will type out your issue. Once you submit it, our staff team will contact you as soon as possible.

__**Bump**__
type </bump:947088344167366698> to bump our server to the top on Disboard

__**Rank Commands**__
- type </rank:1342626366457380951> to know your/member's rank in the server
- type </me:1025501230044286978> to know your stats in the server
- type </user stats:1025501230044286984> to get another members stats in the server 
- type </top:1025501230044286983> to get a list of top users in the server
- type </server:1025501230044286980> to get an overall statistics of the server

onInteraction.content:
**__Music Commands__**
- **Play**
  - </play:1102875264901451826> to play a track/playlist by providing a link/query
  - </nowplaying:1102875265048248364> to show the currently playing track
  - </stop:1102875264901451835> to stop and clear the queue
  - </restart:1102875265048248366> to restart the currently playing track
- **Pause/Unpause**
  - </pause on:1102875264737890353> to pause the currently playing track
  - </pause off:1102875264737890353> to unpause the paused track
- **Repeat**
  - </repeat single:1102875264901451829> to loop the currently playing track
  - </repeat all:1102875264901451829> to loop the queue
  - </repeat off:1102875264901451829> to unloop the track/queue
- **Skip**
  - </skip first:1102875264901451834> skips the current track
  - </skip number:1102875264901451834> skip a certain song in the queue corresponding to its position in queue
